        <updateDate>2019-10-03T16:18:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Space Resources Institute Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) to submit a report on the merits of, and options for, establishing an institute related to space resources in order to advance NASA's objectives for maintaining U.S. preeminence in space. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
